column3: “Very cerebral médicine, not much body stone to it, but a very enjoyable high, no ceilings, happy herb that you can use to medicate all day.”
“this herb is very cerebral, euphoric and energetic, hybrid 70/30 sativa, will help with lack of appetite, insomnia and pain, tested with a GC @ 18.2% THC & 0.3%CBD”
